description: The four people from the previous frame, one woman and three men, still around the whiteboard but now looking at each other, they appear enthusiastic.
The four people from the previous frame, they are now sitting on the floor, one of the men is holding a VR headset, the three others look excited.
The four people wearing the VR headset, they all appear immersed and are smiling widely.
The four people removing the VR headset, they appear amazed and are discussing something animatedly.
The four people now standing in front of a large group of people, one of the men is giving a presentation, the other three are smiling and nodding.
